<div id="review_2004482734" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2004482734" />
    <a title="Denise Kettering" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6587065-denise-kettering"><img alt="Denise Kettering" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2004482734?book_show_action=true">May 19, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Denise Kettering" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Denise Kettering" href="/user/show/6587065-denise-kettering">Denise Kettering</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6587065-denise-kettering?shelf=mystery">mystery</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2004482734" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17744816237717900169">This is a classic Dick Francis novel that incorporates horse-racing into a broader story, in this case about gemstone sales. There is a likeable and successful main character, Derek Franklin, who has to use his natural intellect in order to figure out who is trying to kill him. The story moves along a fast clip and keeps the reader interested throughout. There is suspense that keeps you guessing about what is actually going on under the surface.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


